org.apache.ctakes.utils.xcas_comparison

Class XcasProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.apache.ctakes.utils.xcas_comparison.XcasProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class XcasProcessor
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    A SAX parser that parses an XCAS file. This is done without referencing to the UIMA Type System definition. Therefore, XcasDiff can be used to compare XCASes from different type systems.
